  <brief_title>Evaluation of Effects of Multiple Dose Regimens of CHF 5074 on Potential Biomarkers of Neurodegeneration in Subjects With Mild Cognitive Impairment</brief_title>
  <acronym>CT05</acronym>
  <official_title>A Double-Blind, Randomized, Placebo-Controlled, Multicenter Study to Evaluate the Effects of Multiple Dose Regimens of CHF 5074 for up to 2 Years on Potential Biomarkers of Neurodegeneration in Subjects With Mild Cognitive Impairment</official_title>
