  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      To evaluate the effects of multiple dose regimens of CHF 5074 administered once per day up to
      2 years on potential biomarkers of neurodegeneration in subjects with mild cognitive
      impairment.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
